extendedInfo.description: Kawaii Fruits Theme For Go SMS Pro.Kawaii, Japanese word for Cute, which is a good tag for this theme. Cute fruits in a beautiful green background.Also Download the companion themes. Search for Kawaii Fruits Go Launcher theme and Kawaii Fruits Go Contacts Theme.Developed by the JV-Designs team.-----=====**********=====-----1. You must have GO SMS installed (search "GO SMS" to download).2. To apply the theme within GO SMS: Menu -> Themes -> Choose âKawaii Fruits" theme.-----=====**********=====-----To Activate the theme specific sms popup. Please follow the following directions.1. Open Go SMS pro.2. Press menu3. Select Themes4. Select the Go Popup Tab5. Select the icon below the Go popup tab. Its like 3 horizontal lines.6. Select the "Use the Normal popup" radial optionThat should activate the theme specific sms popup.-----=====**********=====-----Tested on a Samsung Galaxy S2 and a Samsung Galaxy Note.Email us if there are any problems, questions or suggestions.Please rate if you like it. :)

reviews.title: Pretty cute!
reviews.comment: It can be hard to find nice go SMS themes. The images don\'t distort when flipping between horizontal and vertical either. All around cute.
reviews.author: Megan Ryan

reviews.title: Cute!
reviews.comment: Any other colour scheme then green? :D maybe blue or cyan? Any other backgrounds with the fruits in it?

reviews.title: Oh my gosh!
